{"tid":642415,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實侵侵受唔受輸國人歡迎？","createTime":"2018-04-25T18:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T23:58:15.000Z","uid":182475,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e72f7547723717c6bddcff1936b0ed601458686b","tid":642415,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:42:01.000Z","msg":"同「外界」或者香港社會普遍相比，連登的巴絲對侵侵似乎有唔同睇法。咁究竟直接受侵侵政策影響、但又反過來可以繼續選又或者踢走侵侵嘅輸國人又係點睇呢？作為起點，我地就不如用蓋洛普嘅調查嚟睇睇輸國人點睇侵侵。<br />\n<br />\n首先呢個係最常見最普遍被引用的調查：<a href=\"http://news.gallup.com/poll/203198/presidential-approval-ratings-donald-trump.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F203198%2Fpresidential-approval-ratings-donald-trump.aspx&d=IZSyXkB50tSHNF54787tJbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=bce93805\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.gallup.com/poll/203198/presidential-approval-ratings-donald-trump.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n可以見到，侵最新一週支持度係38%，任內平均39%，最高45%，最低35%。對比其他總統佢地任期中嘅同一時間，奧巴馬支持度有48%，小布殊有76%，克林頓就有50%。<strong>比起1938-2018的總統(包括佢自己啦)平均有53%支持度，侵侵真係唔多受歡迎。</strong>同時，佢個支持度同反對度個對照，自17年3月左右起(又或者其實係自開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )都係唔多好，支持度同反對度都係來來去去 38-40% : 55-60%<br />\n<br />\n但係輸國人支持同反對侵侵嘅原因又係點？蓋洛普喺2017年7月有個好過癮的調查(<a href=\"http://news.gallup.com/poll/214091/trump-disapproval-rooted-character-concerns.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F214091%2Ftrump-disapproval-rooted-character-concerns.aspx&d=IZSyXkB50tSHNF54787tJbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=22cf06cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.gallup.com/poll/214091/trump-disapproval-rooted-character-concerns.aspx</a>)。入面問到：輸國人因乜解究而鍾意或唔鍾意侵侵？<br />\n<br />\n個結果其實相當攪鬼。調查發現，<strong>唔支持侵的人當中，有65%係唔鍾意佢性格或個人特質</strong> ，同時因政治或政策相關議題唔like佢，只有16%。相對之下，反對奧巴馬者主要係因為唔支持佢政策相關議題。小布殊呢？原來有43%人唔like佢整體表現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。而後兩者其實都無咩幾多人因為性格或個人特質唔鍾意佢地。<br />\n<br />\n再仔細睇個break down就更加神秘。果65%入面，有29個百份點係因為覺得侵侵唔似有總統個格/臭脾氣/自大/乞人憎而唔like佢，之後亦有10個百份點覺得佢係新手所以唔掂。同時亦有6個百份點嘅人因為佢用Twitter治國而唔like佢。而因為佢性別或種族歧視而唔支持佢，其實只有3個百份點...<br />\n<br />\n政策呢？其實在果16%入面，有4個百份點係「整體但唔多具體地」唔喜歡佢的政策。而其餘果12個百份點呢，就真係講得出因咩政策唔like侵侵啦。<br />\n<br />\n至於支持者呢？調查顯示，其實侵侵同奧巴馬嘅支持永個結構尚算相似。因整體表現、政策、個人特質呢三樣嘢而支持佢地嘅人，比例都約為4:4:2。至於侵侵的支持者中，有相當多係因為佢嘅「商業硬漢」形象而十卜佢。例如在全部支持者中，覺得佢在困難時候會做得好的人有12個百份點，有政治口齒有11百份點，真係會輸國優先有10百份點，不畏縮或會「真。迎難而上」有9百份點，甚至認為因為佢係素人(及有錢佬)而唔會被傳統政治力量都有7百份點。<br />\n<br />\n另外，其實輸國人覺得侵侵攪經濟攪成點？我地又睇下2018年頭幫侵侵做2017的盤點 (<a href=\"http://news.gallup.com/poll/225467/trump-approval-lower-mood-predict.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F225467%2Ftrump-approval-lower-mood-predict.aspx&d=IZSyXkB50tSHNF54787tJbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=9afce9bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.gallup.com/poll/225467/trump-approval-lower-mood-predict.aspx</a>)。<br />\n<br />\n入面指出，侵侵嘅支持率同美國人在經濟問題上對侵侵嘅觀感係甩咗轆的。亦即係話，相對其他數據言，侵侵的支持度其實係被貶抑咗。點解咁講呢？因為：<img src=\"http://content.gallup.com/origin/gallupinc/GallupSpaces/Production/Cms/POLL/i7h31qsmnkkjrg41oc2j9g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcontent.gallup.com%2Forigin%2Fgallupinc%2FGallupSpaces%2FProduction%2FCms%2FPOLL%2Fi7h31qsmnkkjrg41oc2j9g.png&h=eb63af21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就民眾對侵侵任內經濟的滿意度而言，認為美國經濟「優異/良好」及「變得更好」的比率，其實只係比克林頓整個任期低，而贏晒小布殊及奧巴馬兩個人的整個任期。<br />\n<br />\n再另一個調查：<a href=\"http://news.gallup.com/poll/232046/americans-continue-rate-trump-highest-economy.aspx?g_source=link_NEWSV9&amp;g_medium=tile_3&amp;g_campaign=item_203198&amp;g_content=Americans%2520Continue%2520to%2520Rate%2520Trump%2520Highest%2520on%2520Economy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F232046%2Famericans-continue-rate-trump-highest-economy.aspx%3Fg_source%3Dlink_NEWSV9%26g_medium%3Dtile_3%26g_campaign%3Ditem_203198%26g_content%3DAmericans%252520Continue%252520to%252520Rate%252520Trump%252520Highest%252520on%252520Economy&d=IZSyXkB50tSHNF54787tJbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=5908b726\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.gallup.com/poll/232046/americans-continue-rate-trump-highest-economy.aspx?g_source=link_NEWSV9&amp;g_medium=tile_3&amp;g_campaign=item_203198&amp;g_content=Americans%2520Continue%2520to%2520Rate%2520Trump%2520Highest%2520on%2520Economy</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度顯示出，如果同樣拿任期第一年(2017，同年9-10月左右開始宣佈縮表)及第二年(今年)比，侵侵都比起力架做得好。有54%民眾在侵侵任期第一年會比good輸國經濟，去到第二年都仲有46%。相對力架，第一年(2009)有61%人比good佢，而第二年(2010)就得返38% (補充：QE 1 在2008年11月公佈，QE 2 在2010年11月公佈)。不過侵侵在環保及能源議題上，似乎就真係好多人唔like佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n至於今年埋單侵侵在經濟上會拿到幾多分呢？呢個就要睇下贏國贏到有幾開巷，輸國輸得有幾慘烈了。<br />\n<br />\n最後附上一個都幾有趣的調查：<a href=\"http://news.gallup.com/poll/226091/party-ideology-race-play-key-roles-trump-approval.aspx?g_source=link_NEWSV9&amp;g_medium=tile_1&amp;g_campaign=item_203198&amp;g_content=Party%2c%2520Ideology%2520and%2520Race%2520Play%2520Key%2520Roles%2520in%2520Trump%2520Approval\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F226091%2Fparty-ideology-race-play-key-roles-trump-approval.aspx%3Fg_source%3Dlink_NEWSV9%26g_medium%3Dtile_1%26g_campaign%3Ditem_203198%26g_content%3DParty%252c%252520Ideology%252520and%252520Race%252520Play%252520Key%252520Roles%252520in%252520Trump%252520Approval&d=IZSyXkB50tSHNF54787tJbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=66aead68\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.gallup.com/poll/226091/party-ideology-race-play-key-roles-trump-approval.aspx?g_source=link_NEWSV9&amp;g_medium=tile_1&amp;g_campaign=item_203198&amp;g_content=Party%2c%2520Ideology%2520and%2520Race%2520Play%2520Key%2520Roles%2520in%2520Trump%2520Approval</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係講侵侵支持者的黨派取向、意識型態及種族的關係。簡言之，你幾乎可以由果個人的政治取向睇到佢係唔係侵的支持者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充、討論及指正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed31061034d523c47a296f0e9a2445c278f218ad","tid":642415,"uid":93450,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T18:54:54.000Z","msg":"輸國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad095f9c547f73867db3627c5d268029b41127c","tid":642415,"uid":138441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T19:08:10.000Z","msg":"環保撚緊係唔鐘意，一個唔信全球暖化嘅人做總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdd8e47ab6ec6921298c0064ad7c7968e8321b6","tid":642415,"uid":16185,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T19:15:05.000Z","msg":"個人意見係睇支持度無咩意思， trump做緊嘅事比較即時見效，而其他總統做嘅事又可能較為根基同長遠，短期睇好似無政職咁。有即時效果vs 無即時效果 其實好影響支持度，但兩者都可能係好嘅決策。結論，為trump評價言之尚早"},{"pid":"3105f1f544c1a9bd429ce2f9264d955e4e8bf4a7","tid":642415,"uid":6347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T19:24:45.000Z","msg":"其實有外敵個領袖支持度正常都會上升<br />\n所以中國先咁鍾意用美國做假想敵<br />\n佢一直打落去唔縮，一定連到任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acf7bed81ec8efc10ed4d19b98f88ad5f2b3be5","tid":642415,"uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T19:36:44.000Z","msg":"簡單總結一下，有好多人唔支持侵侵係因為佢形象差，但同時又覺得佢經濟政策交到功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係唔鐘意條友，但又覺得條友做到野，囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31003a5468e78d94b9495e7f9f250747ffe065e8","tid":642415,"uid":86587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T19:39:53.000Z","msg":"由trump贏到布拉莉開始，就知道呢啲民調得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c795bb9a13f5c4fb6450d18d827a3d6439a222","tid":642415,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T20:26:37.000Z","msg":"trump should be the most popular and adorable united state president to HK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/9jEaPxN9eZWmI/200w.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F9jEaPxN9eZWmI%2F200w.webp&h=c91b0020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media2.giphy.com/media/xTiTnHXbRoaZ1B1Mo8/200w.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia2.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FxTiTnHXbRoaZ1B1Mo8%2F200w.webp&h=06fa90cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQdYRl7pQtZ-cya1G3_-P2_1V8wHluvv24d_lGO1i6TqbNs6tRMAw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQdYRl7pQtZ-cya1G3_-P2_1V8wHluvv24d_lGO1i6TqbNs6tRMAw&h=b31eaeb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb85b6cd0c5daf8cbb5f39965bc1006315d9c029","tid":642415,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T20:31:46.000Z","msg":"根據我美國親戚講，侵侵真係好受人愛戴，古有泰始王建長城，今有侵侵建圍牆<br />\n<br />\n侵侵名流萬世係註定既"},{"pid":"dbc198800be202316f0102e61429c52303590fc0","tid":642415,"uid":49392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T20:50:35.000Z","msg":"睇落美國人討厭佢嘅原因：<br />\n唔尊重女人<br />\n白人至上主義<br />\n支持擁槍<br />\n破過產幾次嘅賤精生意佬"},{"pid":"87b1825943d6216d3a7e4169ce8acadfc3445dca","tid":642415,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T21:01:27.000Z","msg":"口裏說不 身體卻很誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859270ea3c6284b7794646ccd5110778d120d43f","tid":642415,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T22:55:38.000Z","msg":"俾fake news搞到唔鍾意侵<br />\n但又覺得佢做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c688e5b6450571d332eee19f0915fc080635fb42","tid":642415,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:02:22.000Z","msg":"香港大批大批中年人狂屌美帝唔抵得中國強大攪中興喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多撚到呢"},{"pid":"416f4060eb1c3d4fd8b3318b520f68551139810c","tid":642415,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"